---
import '../styles/global.css'
---
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Enterprise — SessionFS</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@500;600;700;800&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="antialiased" style="color: #e6edf3;">
  <nav style="background: rgba(10,12,16,0.7); backdrop-filter: blur(12px); border-bottom: 1px solid #30363d;" class="fixed top-0 w-full z-50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5 h-16 flex items-center justify-between">
      <a href="/" style="font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans'; font-weight: 600; font-size: 18px;">Session<span style="color: #4f9cf7;">FS</span></a>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-6 text-[15px] font-medium">
        <a href="/docs/" class="text-[#b1b8c1] hover:text-white transition-colors">Docs</a>
        <a href="/pricing/" class="text-[#b1b8c1] hover:text-white transition-colors">Pricing</a>
        <a href="/enterprise/" class="text-white">Enterprise</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <section class="pt-32 pb-20 px-5 noise">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-6" style="font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans';">Deploy anywhere.<br>Control everything.</h1>
        <p class="text-lg max-w-xl mx-auto" style="color: #c9d1d9;">Self-hosted Kubernetes deployment with Helm. Your data stays on your infrastructure. Enterprise-tested on AWS EKS.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-16">
        <div class="glass p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Self-hosted deployment</h3>
          <p class="text-sm mb-4" style="color: #c9d1d9;">Deploy to any Kubernetes cluster — AWS EKS, GCP GKE, Azure AKS, or on-prem. Helm chart with API, MCP, Dashboard, PostgreSQL, and migrations.</p>
          <code class="block text-sm p-3 rounded" style="background: #0a0c10; color: #3ddc84; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;">helm install sessionfs ./charts/sessionfs</code>
        </div>
        <div class="glass p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Data sovereignty</h3>
          <p class="text-sm mb-4" style="color: #c9d1d9;">Your bucket, your database, your infrastructure. Session data never leaves your network. BYOI (Bring Your Own Infrastructure) model.</p>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: #9ca3af;">S3, GCS, or local PVC storage. PostgreSQL (RDS, Cloud SQL, or built-in).</p>
        </div>
        <div class="glass p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">AI governance</h3>
          <p class="text-sm mb-4" style="color: #c9d1d9;">Complete audit trail of every AI agent action. LLM Judge V2 with severity-classified findings. Session summaries for management review.</p>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: #9ca3af;">Auto-audit on sync or PR/MR. Audit history with model comparison.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="glass p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Your LLM gateway</h3>
          <p class="text-sm mb-4" style="color: #c9d1d9;">Bring your own LLM for auditing — Anthropic, OpenAI, Google, or any OpenAI-compatible endpoint. No API keys stored on our servers.</p>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: #9ca3af;">LiteLLM, vLLM, Ollama, Azure OpenAI all supported.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="glass p-8 text-center max-w-lg mx-auto">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Talk to us</h3>
        <p class="text-sm mb-4" style="color: #c9d1d9;">Self-hosted deployment, HIPAA compliance, SAML SSO, SLA, and dedicated support.</p>
        <a href="mailto:enterprise@sessionfs.dev?subject=SessionFS%20Enterprise" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center text-white font-semibold rounded-lg px-7 py-3 hover:brightness-110 transition" style="background: #4f9cf7;">
          Contact Enterprise Sales
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</body>
</html>
